-- KDB confirms ended talks with Lehman
-- 
-- Wed Sep 10, 2008 3:14am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/10/us-lehman-kdb-talks-idUSSEL00025020080910

 

 SEOUL  (Reuters) - Korea Development Bank on Wednesday confirmed talks had ended for now with Lehman Brothers over a possible investment because of disagreement over terms and considering financial market conditions. 

 "We are announcing that we ended talks at this point in time because of a disagreement over conditions of a transaction and considering domestic and foreign financial market conditions," KDB said in a statement. (Reporting by Kim Yeon-hee; Editing by Keiron Henderson)